Speaking to this NPC will allow you to reset your Primary, Secondary, or both jobs. This can be done once per month. 

Note: If you have the Merchant job, your item stocks will be saved but you will not be able to access them without taking Merchant as a Primary or Secondary.
Perfect for warm weather, whether by sea or land, this black garb is designed by Arwen E'lyn and is great for those with quick hands and a quick eye.

((This is an OOC Job System resource. Click to interact.))

Using this station will allow you to "refresh" any old job items that are placed inside, including PLC spawners to be their new 1x1 inventory size.

Note: This will ONLY work for Job System items and will not work on any Job-crafted equippable items or Artificer-crafted storage items. If you have customized the description of your item, it will be undone.

Gems: This will Convert non Job System gems (Sapphire, Emerald, Ruby and Diamond) to their Job System equivalent.
